322.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/soz1665702767322.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/soz1665702767322.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"soz1665702767322\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      line\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"soz1665702767322__line_66399\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Execute a number of ProcScript statements, without called modules.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"soz1665702767322__topic_d19430e1_d19431e1_d19432e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"soz1665702767322__p_d19433e1_d19434e1_d19435e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Line</code> { <var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"soz1665702767322__topic_d13987e1_d13988e1_d13989e1_d13990e1_d13991e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d863679e65\">\n                        \n Arguments\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"soz1665702767322__p_d19439e1_d19440e1_d19441e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>—number of ProcScript instructions to execute, without stepping through called modules. If not specified, one ProcScript statement is executed.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"soz1665702767322__topic_d13992e1_d13993e1_d13994e1_d13995e1_d13996e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d863679e77\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"soz1665702767322__p_d19445e1_d19446e1_d19447e1\">This command considers a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">call</span> statement as a complete unit; the statements in the called module are not stepped trhough individually.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"soz1665702767322__section_xkb_5nb_tcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d863679e89\">Example:</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following command executeds 10 ProcScript statements, treating any\n               called modules as a unit.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"soz1665702767322__pre_kcj_vnb_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">l 10</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/alu1665702767390.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>step</a><p>Execute a number of ProcScript statements.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532101\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532101\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "line Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 16, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 line Execute a number of ProcScript statements, without called modules. Line { Number } Arguments Number —number of ProcScript instructions to execute, without stepping through called modules. If not specified, one ProcScript statement is executed. Description This command considers a call statement as a complete unit; the statements in the called module are not stepped trhough individually. Example: The following command executeds 10 ProcScript statements, treating any called modules as a unit. l 10 Copy Related Links step Execute a number of ProcScript statements. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}